com.chupacadabra.evolution.pool

Class ReadWriteLockCandidatePool

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chupacadabra.evolution.pool.ReadWriteLockCandidatePool
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CandidatePool

    public final class ReadWriteLockCandidatePool
extends Object
implements CandidatePool
    Uses a ReadWriteLock to ensure theadsafety of an underlying pool.

    All methods are read locked except for setCandidate(int, Candidate), which is write-locked.

    This class uses the decorator design pattern.
